title: 'Burning, annoying' - Frank calls for time after 'very bad' Spurs loss
subtitle: "It's pretty evident if no-one gets the time, no-one can turn it around," says Thomas Frank as Spurs beaten at Nottingham Forest.
full_text: "It's pretty evident if no-one gets the time, no-one can turn it around," says Thomas Frank as Spurs beaten at Nottingham Forest.
